#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:56
msgid "How to Contribute for Developers"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:58
msgid "1. Open an issue first"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:60
msgid ""
"Before starting any significant work, open an issue in the relevant "
"repository to describe what you intend to do. This avoids duplicate effort "
"and allows early feedback. For small corrections (typos, broken links, "
"formatting) you can skip straight to a merge request."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:64
msgid "2. Fork the repository"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:66
msgid "Fork the relevant repository to your own GitLab account or namespace."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:68
msgid "3. Create a feature branch"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:70
msgid "Always work on a dedicated branch, never directly on `main` or `acc`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:72
msgid ""
"git checkout acc                          # start from the acceptance "
"branch\n"
"git pull origin acc                       # make sure it is up to date\n"
"git checkout -b feature/your-topic-name  # create your feature branch"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:78
msgid "Branch naming convention:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "Prefix"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "Use for"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "`feature/`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "New content or functionality"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "`fix/`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "Corrections and bug fixes"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "`docs/`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "Documentation-only changes"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "`refactor/`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:80
msgid "Restructuring without content change"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:87
msgid "4. Make your changes"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:89
msgid "Run the documentation site locally while you work:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:91
msgid ""
"python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate\n"
"pip install -r requirements.txt\n"
"mkdocs serve"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:97
msgid "The site is then available at `http://127.0.0.1:8000/`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:99
msgid ""
"For every English page you add or change, also update the corresponding "
"Dutch placeholder under `docs/nl/`. Dutch placeholders use an info "
"admonition linking back to the English source — see any existing file under "
"`docs/nl/` for the correct format."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:103
msgid "5. Commit your changes"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:105
msgid "Follow the [Conventional Commits]{1} specification:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:108
msgid ""
"docs: add troubleshooting section to LDE user guide\n"
"fix: correct broken link in CPSV Editor overview\n"
"feat: add CPRMV API authentication reference page"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:114
msgid "6. Open a merge request"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:116
msgid ""
"Push your branch to your fork and open a merge request against the `acc` "
"branch of the upstream repository."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:119
msgid "git push origin feature/your-topic-name"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:123
msgid "In the merge request description:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:125
msgid "Reference the related issue (`Closes #123`)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:126
msgid "Briefly describe what changed and why"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:127
msgid "Note any follow-up work that is out of scope for this MR"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:129
msgid ""
"Merge requests are reviewed by the maintainer. Feedback is given directly in "
"the MR thread. Once approved, the maintainer merges into `acc` and promotes "
"to `main` as part of the regular release cycle."
msgstr ""

